article.description: — Javante McCoy posted 14 points as Boston University narrowly defeated Lafayette 64-61 on Sunday night.
article.headline: McCoy scores 14 to lift Boston U past Lafayette 64-61
article.linkText: McCoy scores 14 to lift Boston U past Lafayette 64-61
article.story: EASTON, Pa. -- — Javante McCoy posted 14 points as Boston University narrowly defeated Lafayette 64-61 on Sunday night. Walter Whyte had 13 points and eight rebounds for Boston University (3-5, 3-5 Patriot League). Sukhmail Mathon added 12 points and eight rebounds. Jack Hemphill had seven rebounds. E.J. Stephens had 17 points and seven rebounds for the Leopards (5-3, 5-3). Justin Jaworski added 14 points. Tyrone Perry had 13 points and seven rebounds. Dylan Hastings tied a career high with five blocks. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
